			<div id="div-comment-57486" class="comment-body">
				
				<div class="comment-author-avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ea7ae5843c8ae2b2f8a7faa6688cc240?s=32&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fruhlman.com%2Fwp-includes%2Fimages%2Fblank.gif&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' /><span class="avatar-overlay"></span></div>				<div class="comment-content">
