					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>To me the best part about the Thermapen is that they use a thermocouple instead of a thermistor as the sensing element. That means it&#8217;s more accurate (evidenced by the calibration data included with the unit) and rugged than any other food-grade thermometer.</p>
					</div>

