			<div id="div-comment-57470" class="comment-body">
				
				<div class="comment-author-avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e14ec79756622b702fd94dcc44b536e5?s=64&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fruhlman.com%2Fwp-includes%2Fimages%2Fblank.gif&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-64 photo' height='64' width='64' /><span class="avatar-overlay"></span></div>				<div class="comment-content">
