						<p>I&#8217;d like to be the heretic here and say that I don&#8217;t really like supersharp knives. I mean, I sharpen mine twice a year like yer sposeto. and I alway hate working with them for  almost the first month afterwards. Now I&#8217;m not talking dull, but right off the sharpener sharp is too sharp for me. If I need a razor sharp cut, well I have a razor. But I like my chef&#8217;s knife to have a little feel to it that I don&#8217;t get when its razor sharp.</p>
