					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>Hey Chef.<br />
 I have one to which I think has become essential:<br />
-Meat Grinder (manual or Kitchen Aid attachment.)</p>
<p>You need it for quickly working through meat for sausages, as well as a way to reduce exposures to various e.coli recalls that supermarket ground meats have become so well known for. A good manual one could probably deliver a better beating than an iron pan as well.</p>
<p>An optional, but important one:<br />
-Coffee/ Spice Mill for grinding up fresh spices.</p>
<p>D</p>
