					<div class="comment-text">
						<p>in my opinion, the best cast iron skillets being made today are Wagner Ware, an old brand brought back by American Culinary a few years ago. they don&#8217;t have that weird textured surface that Lodge has, and the handles have a more useful shape. the pan i have is very nice to cook with.</p>
					</div>

